headline: Jabil (JBL) Shares At All-Time High Following Strong 2025
summary: Jabil Inc. (NYSE:JBL) is one of the best performing S&P 500 stocks in the last five years. Jabil Inc. (NYSE:JBL) shares reached an all-time high on February 6, 2026, hitting $259.74.
